{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a box with our belongings which had been shipped to us from Germany, originally to France and-- which included our heavy clothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because at the beginning, we didn't need them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was very-- Pappy, I called him-- he-- Pappy was so annoyed with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why do I need the clothes now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I persisted, and he finally said it was all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to this storage facility and we unpacked it, and it really literally saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we discovered that we had purchased-- we had subscribed to the liberal newspapers in France who had all the information what has been going on in Germany during the period we were away, during Nazism.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were atrocities, and they were all available in the rest of the countries, but not in Germany because Germany was a dictatorship.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the news were leaking out to France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- a book and a newspaper we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- I think the book was called which means the torch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it got photos of atrocities of people had come out of camps, or-- or-- we didn't even know about camps at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or had been beaten and so on in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These were substantiated things that were in this particular book, or in the papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We immediately hired a couple people to repack everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This took hours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we got all finished, and I had my winter coat, my dad and I, we hugged each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because if we had gone back, we knew eventually, at that point we realized, we would have to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If we had gone back with that information in those boxes, they would have immediately killed us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And would-- there was no doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
